msg: Upgraded to atomikos 3.8.0 and renamed the property to 'atomikos-transactions-version' which corrects the typo (transactions instead of trascations).

author: juanpablo
msg: Added required files needed to request bundle uploads to OSSRH.
These files must be gpg signed, and the signature must be detached and of ascii armored format.
Finally, the public key used to sign public must be distributed to hkp://pool.sks-keyservers.net/
